{"tid":1663533,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共最新策略 用錢買班死士落黎香港斬人","createTime":"2019-10-19T12:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T12:59:33.000Z","uid":41411,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"376f107d8d51624e66a7c73d9c0dd16f83a53229","tid":1663533,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"比筆安家費班大陸仔落黎香港斬人殺人<br />\n比人拉左又唔洗死刑 又得食有得住<br />\n分分鐘特登放班本身既死刑犯落黎做交換條件 一蚊安家費都唔洗比"},{"pid":"43ba3faeee4dc9a1a13ff40e4265a473be9b5d7d","tid":1663533,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「文宣升級」巴士流動大字報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662724</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wj3z6Ov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwj3z6Ov.jpg&h=9f735918&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"21b77ecde842f21ce6f60cc3ba5bae62068b336a","tid":1663533,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CyMqxkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCyMqxkD.jpg&h=52183db1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea8dde2c5c46d6559981a9de5a8549e260cea9d5","tid":1663533,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"5240d41c93701a8fdba0ec07cb6b38f1f6290295","tid":1663533,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332d8c4ca2e392865e759d11168b8e8be2042bf9","tid":1663533,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"大埔手足當街被劏！要令國際知道！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663444</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫手用twitter retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n向國際講港人響遊行前遭襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的就係要令港人噤聲!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ff814b737aa31f5d40aee889ef4233ed1eb69995","tid":1663533,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:58:31.000Z","msg":"總之有咩事都入警察數"},{"pid":"14d88d702aacff753753e729e6e78e69020dbf61","tid":1663533,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"唔新啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貫作風<br />\n全世界最大嘅黑社會"}]}